5/17 4:11pm
Working today on migrating the Art objects to Art Image. Currently bug hunting the process of saving collection info when transfering, as it's a large part of our old setup. While this could be done automatically and would save some hassle, I insist on taking days to do it piece by piece. At least this way, I'm troubleshooting errors that might have come up in the move, but I'm also forced to spend extra energy accomodating both patterns. This will be a good move when it's done. I'm finally seeing art collections with art images, so it might be time to set fire on an automated routine.

